reviews.text:
Pool restaurant located on the 2/F inside the sports center, and it is nice and decent restaurant, great place for lunch.
As Pool restaurant no located on street and less promotion at all, it's not a popular restaurant at all, which is actually great as you can easily find a table during lunch peak time.   Their set lunch is budget friendly, and it's come with Chinese soup.  Food here is not great, but it's decent, and staffs are friendly.  You can also have the pool view inside the restaurant.
For lunch, you have to pay in the cashier, before you find your seat
Reasonable price with comparable services aka self service (in lunch hour)
Taste good with very bargain price~
Excellent food! I love the foods and crews. Their service and smile were so nice.

reviews.text: 🤣讚
草滚場冷氣维修後，唔夠冷氣，開多2把風扇，熱得狠
地方細，人多要排隊等入，冷氣不夠
場地沒問題，但職員十分沒禮貌。我們租用上午9至10羽毛球場，在10點時，更衣室正在清潔，讓前一場及下一場的租場人士都非常不便（本身更衣室設計都非常有問題，只能容納三、四個人更衣）。租場人士在外靜候，有其他工作人員催促在內清潔的工人，但清潔工非常不滿地表示還未可以。到大概10:15 ，清潔工出來，大力把圍欄拍向牆壁，並對在場等候人士報以非常不滿的眼光。
我在這裏玩健身有機會我們可以碰一碰面
